#### Myx Nargis Ruba

**Myx Nargis Ruba** (neutral evil, orc **noble**) is one of Zenia's parents and also a King of Coin. Nargis is overseer of the Tavern Keepers Trade and spends much of their time at the Thornapple, the centerpiece of their family's fortune.

When the Kings of Coin made their bargain with the witch Proud Edun to magically cultivate the jeli flower, Nargis convinced the other Kings of Coin they could save their firstborn children by murdering the witch. For five years, Nargis took great pride in the city's success, but the attack on Zenia threatens to expose their lies.

Nargis is a stylishly dressed, middle-aged orc with a stout build. They switch between a posh Zindanese accent and a laborer's gruff lilt depending on whom they talk to.

***Personality Trait.*** "I consider all to be my dearest companions unless proven wrong threeÃ¢ÂÂperhaps fourÃ¢ÂÂtimes."

***Ideal.*** "Family is more important than all the gold in Zinda."

***Bond.*** "I would cheat and kill to keep my daughter with me, but I fear I will lose her as a result."

