#### Amanisha Manivarshi

**Amanisha Manivarshi** is an accomplished dancer and the most recent champion of the Shankha Trials. Known as Nisha to her friends and fans, she is a charming young woman whose Manivarshi ancestors settled in Tippurika after their home disappeared. Nisha uses the last name "Manivarshi" out of respect for her family and heritage.

***Personality Trait.*** "Many see my focus and assume I'm not approachable. But I welcome new friends."

***Ideal.*** "I will make the city of my birth and descendants of Manivarsha proud by bringing home the Riverine's Shankha."

***Bond.*** "The folk of the Manivarshi diaspora cling too much to memories. I will give them something new to celebrate."

