- Adirohit has been locked away for hundreds of years beneath a mighty mangrove that once adorned a temple built in his honorÃ¢ÂÂever since the Shankha Trials that precipitated the destruction of Manivarsha.
- Jijibisha trapped him here using her fiendish power and forced him to cause the flood in Sagorpur.
