***Zhong Yin.*** Zhong Yin is shocked at Secretary Wei's betrayal. From this point on, the spy is willing to aid the characters and will share any information in the "What's Left Unsaid" section earlier in the adventure.

***Stone Defenders.*** After the image of Secretary Wei fades, a sculpted soldier detaches from its alcove, then steps forward to attack. The soldier uses the **stone golem** stat block, except that its Slam action deals slashing damage because it wields a giant glaive.

